# Project Instructions

The project coding standards and AI agent instructions are maintained in a single
canonical file to avoid duplication:

**`.github/instructions/project.instructions.md`**

Always read and follow the instructions in that file when working in this repository.
It covers: code style, architecture patterns, testing standards, documentation rules,
and common tasks.

# PR Review Agent Kit

This repository includes reusable PR review agents under `.github/agents/` and
specialised skills under `.github/skills/`.

Key commands: `full review`, `quick review`, `security review`, `resolve PR comments`.
